data.description: Back on the Market, Turnkey, Ready for immediate move in. Beautiful 4 bedroom 3 bath home with large back yard, located in The Preserve at Riverview. Home offers an open split floor plan with formal dining area & ceramic tile throughout living areas and carpet in the bedrooms. Kitchen has Granite countertops, with a breakfast bar, and eat in area. Laundry room is right off the kitchen for easy access and entrance to the garage. Cabinets in the Kitchen offers roll out shelving. Bathrooms feature granite countertops. Jack and Jill bedroom/bathroom set up is convenient between bedroom 2 & 3 . Master bedroom is spacious with walk in closet. Master bathroom has dual sinks, shower stall, and separate garden bath tub. Enjoy the premium lot view from your open back patio near the culdesac end for minimal traffic. Roof offers radiant barrier for high efficiency & hot water heater is an energy efficient unit that helps keep electric costs down. Location provides for easy access to a major highways and interstate systems and provides easy access to local shopping & dining.
